high_descs: Turn right, walk around to the sink
Open the left door of the top cabinet, Take the yellow sponge out of the cabinet, close the cabinet
Turn around, walk to the stove
Put the sponge in the pan on the right
Take the whole pan on the stove
Turn around, walk to the green table
Put the pan at the edge of the table
anns.task_desc: Grab the sponge from the cabinet, move the sponge with the pan from stove to the table

high_descs: Walk around the table and forward to the sink.
Open the top left cabinet above the sink and take out the sponge.
Turn right and walk to the oven.
Place the sponge in the right pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the table.
Place the pot on the left edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking to the wall, then hang a left and walk around the kitchen island to the sink and look up.
Open the left door of the upper cabinets and remove the sponge.
Turn around and walk over to the oven.
Place the sponge in the pan on the stove that is on the front right burner.
Pick up the pan with sponge in it.
Turn around and walk over to the middle of the kitchen island.
Place the pan with the sponge in it on the left end of the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a sponge in it on the kitchen island.
